{"tid":1432863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好講「過期催淚彈」，試著講「山埃彈」、「毒氣彈」","createTime":"2019-08-08T10:42:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T09:52:32.000Z","uid":293012,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5a649dbe970892b4e10e9d52e3a872c0f2f534e8","tid":1432863,"uid":293012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:42:40.000Z","msg":"藍色人形豬日日「暴徒暴徒」，「廢青廢青」咁鳩叫，搞到佢地鳩上腦，當晒200萬人都係暴徒廢青，我地要以其人之道，還治其人之身！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">點解要咁做！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />洗腦！（老共最鐘意標籤人）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要比大家一個觀感，就係山埃彈好撚嚴重！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「過期催淚彈」拗口囉<br />\n<br />\n點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一齊改名以正視聽啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb42124368926c1402ae37dc917861b028062965","tid":1432863,"uid":293012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:43:27.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"4d4f1dffe599a1f424ebe39ca413ad940082213b","tid":1432863,"uid":293012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:44:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a1db601df41f216562ab3bcee0f6e9914deecb00","tid":1432863,"uid":293012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:48:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4321202c9fec7a37c0f368cd4f1e4fe78963c90a","tid":1432863,"uid":60611,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:49:27.000Z","msg":"毒氣彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e668e97f84c151cc161afae7039be00eaac2212","tid":1432863,"uid":171718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:49:56.000Z","msg":"毒氣<img src=\"/as